<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>dmwʿy̱ fy̱ ạlmkẖạdʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dmwʿy fy ạlmkẖạdʿ lyhạ ʿndk tqdyr
 wḥdk lạ̉hạty sạmʿ wfy ydk ạltdbyr
 qrạr
 wlạ̉nk ạ̉ʿẓm ạb ḥạss bkl mạ fy
 wbttʿạml bạlḥb mʿ ạy jrwḥ mkẖfyh

[V2]
 qlby qạṣdk wḍạrʿ ạtdkẖl yạ qdyr
 shl ʿdy̱ ạlmwạnʿ sẖyl ʿny ạy nyr

[V3]
 ʿạrf ạnk fy ṣfy ḍd qwy̱ ạlsẖryr
 tʿạlj bạlnʿmh ḍʿfy tḥly ḥlqy ạlmryr

[V4]
 tʿbt kẖlạṣ wrạjʿ ạnạ llḥḍn ạlkbyr
 ạsẖfyny mn ạlmwạjʿ wạṣnʿ fyạ ạltgẖyyr</lyrics>
</song>